and top programs!","name":"Arts and Culture Scholarships in Turkey: Best Opportunities","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-arts-and-culture-scholarships/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-arts-and-culture-scholarships/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/arts-and-culture-fellowships-in-turkey.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-arts-and-culture-scholarships/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="art-and-culture-education-in-turkey-why-preferred">Art and Culture Education in Turkey: Why Preferred?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey is a paradise for foreign students who want to study <strong>art and culture</strong>, with its cultural richness that has been filtered through thousands of years of history. It offers a wide range of art from Ottoman to Seljuk, from modern contemporary art galleries to traditional handicrafts.<br>When I first came to Istanbul, I felt that art was breathing everywhere, from the graffiti on the streets to the miniatures in Topkapı Palace. I think that&#8217;s why Turkey is a really strong choice for <strong>art and culture education</strong>.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="turkeys-power-in-arts-and-culture">Turkey&#8217;s Power in Arts and Culture</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In Turkey, art is not just something that hangs on the walls of museums; it is something that is alive, on the streets, in the life itself. Cities like Istanbul, Ankara and Izmir in particular are overflowing with major art festivals, biennials and international exhibitions.<br>World prestigious events offer students not only education, but also real experience and networking opportunities.<br>It is much easier to take part in these events if you participate in an education program supported by <strong>art and culture scholarships</strong>.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="advantages-for-foreign-students">Advantages for Foreign Students</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">There are various privileges for international students who want to study <strong>art and culture</strong> in Turkey:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Increase in English education programs</li>



<li>Cost-effective living and education expenses</li>



<li>Special art and culture scholarships for international students</li>



<li>Possibility of internship in art galleries, theaters, cultural events</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Thanks to these opportunities, arts education in Turkey offers an excellent ground for both academic and professional development.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-are-art-and-culture-scholarships-in-turkey">What are Art and Culture Scholarships in Turkey?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Arts and culture scholarships in Turkey stand out with a wide range of opportunities offered by both state-funded and private institutions. Moreover, these scholarships do not only cover tuition fees; most of them also include living expenses, accommodation and even health insurance.<br>If you want to study in Turkey with art and culture scholarships, it is very important to apply to the right program.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The table below shows the most prominent types of arts and culture scholarships:</p>


<figure class="wp-block-table">
<table class="has-fixed-layout">
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Type of Scholarship</th>
<th>Providing Institution</th>
<th>Scope</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Turkey Scholarships Art Program</td>
<td>T.R. Presidency of the Republic</td>
<td>Education + Accommodation + Salary</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>University Based Art Scholarships</td>
<td>Private and Foundation Universities</td>
<td>Education Fee + Partial Accommodation</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Foundation and Association Scholarships</td>
<td>Vehbi Koç Foundation, Suna-İnan Kıraç Foundation</td>
<td>Education + Project Support</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</figure>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For more details, check out <a href="https://www.turkiyeburslari.gov.tr/tamzamanlibursprogram" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Best Art and Culture Scholarship Programs in Turkey</a>.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="scholarships-offered-by-the-state">Scholarships Offered by the State</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">One of the most comprehensive arts and culture scholarships is offered by the Turkey Scholarships program. This program provides full scholarships to foreign students applying for master&#8217;s, doctoral or art specialization programs.<br>For up-to-date information on application dates and criteria, you can find details on the <a class="" href="https://turkiyeburslari.gov.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">official website</a>.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="scholarship-opportunities-provided-by-private-universities">Scholarship Opportunities Provided by Private Universities</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Many foundations and private universities in Turkey offer arts and culture scholarships to talented foreign students. Institutions such as Istanbul Bilgi University, Sabancı University and Mimar Sinan University of Fine Arts offer scholarships ranging from 25% to 100%.<br>In addition, some schools offer extra scholarships to students who show high achievement in art talent exams.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="application-criteria-and-required-documents">Application Criteria and Required Documents</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Although the details vary depending on the type of scholarship you want to apply for, in general, certain documents and criteria are required.<br>I completed my documents on time during the application process, but my friend almost lost his scholarship chance when he tried to complete a document at the last minute. So preparation is very important!</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="who-can-apply">Who can apply?</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Foreign students wishing to study art full-time in Turkey</li>



<li>High school diploma (for bachelor&#8217;s degree) or university diploma (for master&#8217;s/doctorate)</li>



<li>Usually under the age of 30 (depending on the program)</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Before you apply, I recommend you take a look at <a>Points to Consider When Applying for a Scholarship in Turkey</a>.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="documents-and-application-process">Documents and Application Process</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The basic documents required when applying are as follows:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Passport photocopy</li>



<li>Diploma and transcripts (English or Turkish translation)</li>



<li>Art portfolio (painting, sculpture, photography, etc.)</li>



<li>Letter of intent</li>



<li>Letters of reference</li>



<li>Foreign language proficiency certificate (English or Turkish depending on the program)</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Applications are usually made online and selected applicants may be called for an interview.<br>Example processes for Turkey Scholarships can also be found in <a class="" href="https://turkiyeburslari.gov.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">this resource</a>.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="which-arts-and-culture-fields-can-you-get-a-scholarship-for">Which Arts and Culture Fields Can You Get a Scholarship For?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The world of art and culture is so vast that it is possible to find a scholarship program for almost every field in Turkey. It is very important to choose the right field to apply for because some scholarships are only available for certain art branches.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Here are the main fields of arts and culture that offer scholarships in Turkey:</p>


<figure class="wp-block-table">
<table class="has-fixed-layout">
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Field</th>
<th>Sample Departments</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Visual Arts</td>
<td>Painting, Sculpture, Photography, Graphic Design</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Stage Arts</td>
<td>Theater, Dance, Opera, Ballet</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Music</td>
<td>Classical Music, Modern Music, Musicology</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Traditional Turkish Arts</td>
<td>Hat, Illumination, Miniature, Tile</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Cultural Studies</td>
<td> Folklore, Art History, Cultural Heritage Management</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</figure>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You can find the scholarship that best suits your interests by looking at this table.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="visual-arts-painting-sculpture-photography">Visual Arts (Painting, Sculpture, Photography)</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you are interested in visual arts, many scholarship options await you at institutions such as Mimar Sinan Fine Arts University or Anadolu University. A strong portfolio is a big advantage here.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="stage-arts-theater-dance-music">Stage Arts (Theater, Dance, Music)</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Schools such as the Ankara State Conservatory and Istanbul University State Conservatory lead the way in performing arts scholarships. Turkey is especially ambitious in theater and classical music.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="cultural-studies-and-traditional-arts">Cultural Studies and Traditional Arts</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you want to study Traditional Turkish Arts, schools like Marmara University in Istanbul or <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/selcuk-universitesi-tanitim-kampus-rehberi/">Selçuk University</a> in Konya can offer you great opportunities.<br></p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="the-best-art-and-culture-scholarship-programs-in-turkey">The Best Art and Culture Scholarship Programs in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">So which scholarship programs really stand out? There are a few strong programs in Turkey that you will hear about often when looking for scholarships in the field of arts and culture.<br>Here are some of the best:</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="turkey-scholarships-art-program">Turkey Scholarships Art Program</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">This program, provided by Turkey Scholarships (YTB), provides full support to foreign students who want to pursue a master&#8217;s and PhD in the arts. The program includes tuition fees, dormitory accommodation, health insurance and a monthly stipend.<br>For more information, visit the <a class="" href="https://turkiyeburslari.gov.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">official website</a>.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="university-based-art-scholarships">University Based Art Scholarships</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Some universities run their own scholarship programs. For example:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Istanbul Bilgi University International Art Scholarship</li>



<li>Sabancı University Visual Arts and Visual Communication Design Scholarships</li>



<li>Hacettepe University Faculty of Arts Merit Scholarships</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">These scholarships are usually awarded based on aptitude test results or academic achievement.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="scholarships-of-private-foundations-and-organizations">Scholarships of Private Foundations and Organizations</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Some private foundations in Turkey also provide art and culture scholarships:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Vehbi Koç Foundation Art Scholarships</li>



<li>Suna and İnan Kıraç Foundation Cultural Heritage Support Program</li>



<li>Istanbul Foundation for Culture and Arts (IKSV) Young Artist Support Fund</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The scholarships offered by these foundations are sometimes not limited to financial support, but can also include participation in exhibitions, festivals and events.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="step-now-to-start-your-dream-art-education">Step Now to Start Your Dream Art Education!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">So far, you have learned in detail what it takes to find art and culture scholarships in Turkey. You are now more aware of the application criteria, the areas where you can find scholarships and the most prestigious programs.<br>If you really want to live your passion for art and gain international experience, studying in Turkey can be a great step for you.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Applications open at certain times every year, so it is very important not to miss the process. You can take the first step through the <a>Road to Study Application Guide</a> and find the most suitable art scholarship for you by meeting one-on-one with our counseling team.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Remember, for someone with a passion for art, the right environment and support can make all the difference. Now is the time to act!</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2025-07-29T10:28:21Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2026-03-15T18:46:55Z', "featured_image" = '{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/arts-and-culture-fellowships-in-turkey.webp","alt":"Art and culture scholarships in Turkey","title":"arts-and-culture-fellowships-in-turkey"}' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'turkey-arts-and-culture-scholarships';
